# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/mariq1.rpy:12
translate chinese mariq1_3507eaf6:

    # fr "What are you going to school for?"
    fr "你在读什么专业？"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/mariq1.rpy:13
translate chinese mariq1_35f5e1d3:

    # pc "Quantum Physics."
    pc "量子物理。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/mariq1.rpy:15
translate chinese mariq1_8e0b1b4e:

    # fr "Wow!"
    fr "哇！"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/mariq1.rpy:17
translate chinese mariq1_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/mari_quantum.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari_quantum.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/mariq1.rpy:18
translate chinese mariq1_a7523fa8:

    # fr "What the heck is a quantum?"
    fr "“量子”到底是什么？"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/mariq1.rpy:19
translate chinese mariq1_7df397aa:

    # pc "Well, it's a way to describe the smallest piece of a thing."
    pc "嗯，这是用来描述事物最微小单元的概念。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/mariq1.rpy:21
translate chinese mariq1_d8ac32d6:

    # fr "I don't get it."
    fr "我还是没明白。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/mariq1.rpy:22
translate chinese mariq1_c63b8c2d:

    # pc "Okay, picture a tree. You know how it's made up of branches that spread out in all different directions?"
    pc "这样，想象一棵树。你知道树是由向各个方向伸展的树枝组成的吧？"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/mariq1.rpy:25
translate chinese mariq1_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice 'voices/mari_yep.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari_yep.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/mariq1.rpy:26
translate chinese mariq1_38aded6c:

    # fr "Yep."
    fr "是的。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/mariq1.rpy:27
translate chinese mariq1_7ef6575d:

    # pc "And all of those branches grow leaves on them."
    pc "而且所有树枝上都长着叶子。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/mariq1.rpy:28
translate chinese mariq1_d14500f6:

    # pc "And if you look at those leaves, there's branches on them too, little veins that go in every direction."
    pc "如果你仔细看那些叶子，上面也有分支，就是那些向各个方向延伸的细小叶脉。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/mariq1.rpy:29
translate chinese mariq1_275848aa:

    # pc "Now you can't see it, but if you put those leaves under a microscope, you would be able to see that those branches break up even further."
    pc "虽然肉眼看不见，但如果你把这些叶子放在显微镜下观察，就会发现那些枝条还会进一步分支。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/mariq1.rpy:30
translate chinese mariq1_5ce2b371:

    # pc "And if you keep zooming in further and further, you would see the smallest piece of that leaf, where it doesn't break down any further."
    pc "如果你继续不断放大，最终会看到叶子最小的部分，那里再也无法分解了。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/mariq1.rpy:31
translate chinese mariq1_7fe9dbc9:

    # pc "The individual atom that makes up every thing in existence. That's what I'm studying."
    pc "那个构成万物的单个原子。这就是我正在研究的。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/mariq1.rpy:33
translate chinese mariq1_5953bbc9:

    # fr "Wow. That's incredible."
    fr "哇。太不可思议了。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/mariq1.rpy:34
translate chinese mariq1_1894d6a7:

    # pc "It's not that big a deal. You're going to be a vet. You're going to save animals. I'm just going to look at their atoms."
    pc "也没什么大不了的。你要当兽医，去拯救动物。而我只是研究它们的原子。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/mariq1.rpy:36
translate chinese mariq1_b91e3471:

    # fr "You're right. It's not that impressive when you put it like that."
    fr "你说得对。这么一说确实没那么厉害。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/mariq1.rpy:37
translate chinese mariq1_093307bf:

    # fr "Still, thanks for explaining it to me. It's pretty neat."
    fr "不过还是谢谢你给我解释。挺有意思的。"

